{"id": 606, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都是怎么做旅行攻略的？", "description": "在上班的间隙摸鱼刷机票什么的。", "record_count": 2129, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201606071946526x5mCLz0G78IA3yB.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-29T10:25:29Z", "options": [{"id": 20992, "content": "每次出行都是老公做攻略、结果……就是没攻略", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248413}, {"id": 20994, "content": "啥都不用准备，带个老婆，就啥都有了", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274395}, {"id": 20997, "content": "省钱先", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274465}, {"id": 20998, "content": "不能考虑太多，因为考虑的太多就不想去了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215666}, {"id": 20999, "content": "到了一个地方先去官方旅游局拿免费地图 再拿感兴趣的活动或者景点介绍册子 跟着地图上显示的景点走 （旅游业发达地区适用）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260601}, {"id": 21000, "content": "想想自己要一个什么样的旅行，然后在地图上找哪里是自己没有去过的，定三四个目的地，看机票火车票各种交通票，选择最便宜的！ 然后定行程，本着不走回头路，不累成?的原则。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252597}, {"id": 21513, "content": "好像大家素质都不高", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265403}, {"id": 21002, "content": "为了做路线把伦敦一区画了出来，精确到分。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255658}, {"id": 21003, "content": "我就负责带人去，其他不要管", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274555}, {"id": 20748, "content": "我会收藏旅游微信公众号推荐的小众景点", "image": null, "praise_count": 103, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 21004, "content": "旅游是什么能吃吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 180917}, {"id": 20749, "content": "想好了去一个地方先看看马蜂窝", "image": null, "praise_count": 426, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 21005, "content": "做毛线攻略，到了目的地再想怎么办，我向来是这样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269761}, {"id": 20750, "content": "定期刷廉航机票", "image": null, "praise_count": 93, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 20751, "content": "关注穷游的优惠自由行或者机票酒店组合", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 20752, "content": "上面包旅行看游记", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 21008, "content": "先确定要去的景点，再查交通。其他都好说", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211441O5mXCplrDitFzv3J.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253289}, {"id": 20753, "content": "听朋友推荐，去TA去过的景点", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 21009, "content": "先订好票到那里再说，不然很容易泡汤(ーー゛)", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227136}, {"id": 21010, "content": "记录有啥东西玩和吃，然后算行程……选几个感兴趣的地方去，地点与地点停留时间预留多点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241374}, {"id": 21011, "content": "主要先是买机票和订酒店?", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215032}, {"id": 21013, "content": "主要靠老公?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273177}, {"id": 21014, "content": "没去过又觉得可以去的地方廉价机票就去，然后找游记看看定几个必去的点，其它就闲逛，然后以交通便利为首要原则定房，然后就出发了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258694}, {"id": 21018, "content": "出境游用游谱旅行", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274712}, {"id": 21530, "content": "先百度了解地区，然后定制计划", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278470}, {"id": 21277, "content": "带好钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267350}, {"id": 21023, "content": "下个APP 然后就没有然后了 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262896}, {"id": 21535, "content": "各种网站上找适合自己的攻略，跟朋友和家人交流。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278522}, {"id": 21024, "content": "在各种APP上签到，领红包，攒积分。刷去哪儿的便宜机票。计算跟团走还是自由行合适。（景点门票+住宿+交通费）。规划最短游玩路线，有限时间看更多风景！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193525}, {"id": 21027, "content": "度娘", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 220362}, {"id": 21029, "content": "看心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253323}, {"id": 21030, "content": "找一个男盆友ฅ(⌯͒•̩̩̩́ ˑ̫ •̩̩̩̀⌯͒)ฅ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274821}, {"id": 21031, "content": "平时关注旅游相关的资讯，不一定会事先所有细节都安排好，但是得把需要去的景点，在哪里吃东西，玩耍时间，如何到达目的地，再如何去另外一个景点确定，然后安排一个最佳路线（不走重复路）。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 96631}, {"id": 21032, "content": "软文………", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242981}, {"id": 21034, "content": "看那里人少，但是风景非常棒的那种没有多少商业气息的地方。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274861}, {"id": 21035, "content": "看杂志推荐", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274853}, {"id": 21554, "content": "去哪儿看看机票，蚂蜂看看攻略，QQ侃侃大山。其实到地方我是迷茫的，就瞎玩儿吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278955}, {"id": 21046, "content": "一个人查攻略，一个人当小弱智。我是后面那个。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274910}, {"id": 21048, "content": "随心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232200}, {"id": 21050, "content": "首先，确定旅伴，敲定同行时间。然后立刻打开去哪儿预定机票，打开airbnb定民宿。其次登陆马蜂窝，记下想去的地方以及这个行程约花费多久时间（希望旅伴也同时做这件事）。再次问一下已经去过旅行目的地或者在该地生活的朋友哪些行程是可以完全pass的。最后，带上一份标记了预估行程和行程花费时间的地图和小伙伴一起随意的走，并不会每个行程都去，但一定会尽兴并且省掉很多冤", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268610}, {"id": 21051, "content": "搜，问，订，碰。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194381}, {"id": 21055, "content": "结实本地人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 198497}, {"id": 21057, "content": "不做计划，走到那算那。", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211517r4VT9nAjXkLplv57.jpg", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274971}, {"id": 21061, "content": "先去再说", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274991}, {"id": 21064, "content": "先攻略，再确定路线，订房安排好日程，gogogo!", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 275002}, {"id": 23112, "content": "先定要去的几个地方，然后时间，最后看攻略怎么玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290682}, {"id": 21325, "content": "先想好去哪", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250844}, {"id": 21841, "content": "蚂蜂窝 百度 携程 淘宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281346}, {"id": 23889, "content": "都是看哪里比较有好玩的几个点，有什么吃的，看有没有旅伴……之后就订机票订酒店，攻略是大概的，去到那里再变动一下～喜欢搭当地公交地铁逛超市吃排队美食。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294364}, {"id": 21077, "content": "最先想好要去哪里，然后看别人的攻略再根据自己的情况和最想做的事制定计划，提前在网上订好酒店，就和朋友出发了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260441}]}